Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Cannot parse plist file

Solution: Verify file format with file command; ensure it's valid XML or binary plist
Issue: SQLite database locked

Solution: Close any open connections; use .timeout command in sqlite3
Issue: Python script fails with import errors

Solution: Verify Python 3 is used; plistlib is built-in, no installation needed
Issue: No sensitive data found

Solution: Check pattern matching logic; verify data exists in source files
